ryone that is training skill points in Disarm - STOP!<br>
<br>
I went from level 35 (1 point dumped into it) to level 160 in about 8 hours of play time and it didn't cost me a cent.  The fastest way to raise the skill is as follows:<br>
<br>
Get a non-magical weapon.  Find an orc pawn. Give it the weapon. Take your weapon(s) out of your hands in case you riposte. Disarm the heck out of the pawn.  Disarm is one of the few skills that will raise on greens.  If you do manage to riposte the pawn, sit down, let it heal and keep going.  If you disarm it, kill the pawn and go find another one.  This technique can also be used with other similar low level mobs that don't agro (i.e., decaying skeleton).<br>
<br>
You can even prevent ripostes alltogether by turning your back on the mob you're disarming then facing it for riposte and turning back around.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps! <p>Nuke 'em til they glow, then shoot 'em in the dark!<br>
